Consider the following vectors:

\begin{tikzpicture}
\draw[->] (0,0) -- (2,0) node[right] {$\vec{a} = 2\hat{i}$};
\draw[->] (0,0) -- (0,2) node[above] {$\vec{b} = 2\hat{j}$};
\draw[dashed] (2,0) -- (2,2) -- (0,2);
\end{tikzpicture}

Find:
a) The magnitude of $\vec{a} + \vec{b}$
b) The angle between $\vec{a}$ and $\vec{a} + \vec{b}$
